{"tid":985403,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"波台冇人講比爾沙開 lecture？","createTime":"2019-01-17T14:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T11:25:29.000Z","uid":36324,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"5acc37de68ea248ca2e8140f447bc19d1fb3063f","tid":985403,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T14:17:52.000Z","msg":"成件事都好撚傳奇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67bd9da146a4977cffec6ce05b2ea490cdb43b49","tid":985403,"uid":36324,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:13:32.000Z","msg":"笑死<br />\n先係無違法地 &quot;spy&quot; 林伯隊打比 (所謂 spy 係由公眾地方用望遠鏡望)<br />\n然後林伯投訴、傳媒起鬨<br />\n比爾沙就開記者會<br />\n<br />\n以為會辭職，點知就開 lecture，70版 powerpoint slides<br />\n真係 show 自己極度瘋狂既 work ethics，公開詳細剖識林伯隊波，證明自己本身唔洗靠 &quot;spying&quot; 都已經對其他球隊認識好深<br />\n夠膽做夠膽認，講明自己每隊英冠都 &quot;spy&quot; 過，甚至承認道德上可能 &quot;spying&quot; 唔係幾好，但指出係無違反任何清晰訂明既規則 <br />\n跟住又話其實做左咁多準備，&quot;spying&quot; 可能都無咩用，只不過係如果有D野有空間做 (無違法) 而無做到，自己會覺得內咎，所以點都做埋<br />\n<br />\n出左黎既效果竟然仲要係扭轉民意，令好多英人都俾呢種工作熱誠同對足球既迷戀執著折服；成功表現到自己係一個所有合法方式都會利用既認真工作狂  (英人最 buy 呢D) + 公開透明唔介意認錯同解釋行為始末緣由既成年人；反而搞到林伯好似小學雞日日單單打打咁；另外仲成功令人質疑足總D規則點解 draft 得咁空泛，無辦法清楚了解有D咩行為係禁止"},{"pid":"b4ac5f6d6e50c685a47e50bea1d11cce2a0817d6","tid":985403,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:16:36.000Z","msg":"講多D"},{"pid":"4b616f1d962d262076812e55bb2823c5a40c2eb4","tid":985403,"uid":4322,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:21:46.000Z","msg":"其實好痴線 好落力去做分析 respect"},{"pid":"e0c3d2992dfa56c04f24ca6041f14bc5e1b2c00b","tid":985403,"uid":31151,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:35:23.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 邊場波邊個踢咩位幾時會轉陣 球員舉手係咩意思都分析晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8bc2aae037c5d986dbf827733e56e4e7d9e17de","tid":985403,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:42:16.000Z","msg":"林伯心理戰算唔算成功左"},{"pid":"7abd2d0711cc7065afc393b7571eb9df4b114fdc","tid":985403,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:42:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/football/video/2019/jan/17/i-observed-all-the-rivals-we-played-marcelo-bielsas-spygate-presentation-video\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ffootball%2Fvideo%2F2019%2Fjan%2F17%2Fi-observed-all-the-rivals-we-played-marcelo-bielsas-spygate-presentation-video&d=IXeaUj7MBsH%2FpAjUoWaQHDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=0fe39a9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/football/video/2019/jan/17/i-observed-all-the-rivals-we-played-marcelo-bielsas-spygate-presentation-video</a>"},{"pid":"3f2caed06e68d88873420374135aee0aabf5a8b9","tid":985403,"uid":4170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:47:25.000Z","msg":"有冇佢份PPT睇下?"},{"pid":"70659e29437003804cd7c330380d4f051e50acb3","tid":985403,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4ac5f6d6e50c685a47e50bea1d11cce2a0817d6","tid":985403,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:16:36.000Z","msg":"講多D"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:49:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/46896639\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2F46896639&d=IXeaUj7MBsH%2FpAjUoWaQHDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=9cfe12ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/46896639</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/football/2019/jan/17/marceo-bielsa-spygate-powerpoint-leeds-united\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ffootball%2F2019%2Fjan%2F17%2Fmarceo-bielsa-spygate-powerpoint-leeds-united&d=IXeaUj7MBsH%2FpAjUoWaQHDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B