<a href=\"https://www.theweek.co.uk/football/99037/leeds-derby-spygate-marcelo-bielsa-powerpoint-presentation-best-tweets-reactions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.co.uk%2Ffootball%2F99037%2Fleeds-derby-spygate-marcelo-bielsa-powerpoint-presentation-best-tweets-reactions&d=IXeaUj7MBsH%2FpAjUoWaQHDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=75da4714\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theweek.co.uk/football/99037/leeds-derby-spygate-marcelo-bielsa-powerpoint-presentation-best-tweets-reactions</a><br />\nsocial media reactions <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/46906415\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2F46906415&d=IXeaUj7MBsH%2FpAjUoWaQHDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ceaf8a85\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/46906415</a><br />\n<br />\nBBC 認真分析 what we learned<br />\n1) The &quot;incomprehensible&quot; scale and depth of preparation<br />\n2) Awareness of how footballers work<br />\n3) Respect for opponents<br />\n4) Bielsa's idiosyncrasies<br />\n5) 'You know more about Barcelona than me'"},{"pid":"e4eb741c45f721a65190355718e66011fe98030e","tid":985403,"uid":36324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:59:55.000Z","msg":"從報導所講，比爾沙最起碼會分析曬對手每個戰術 (同用過幾多次)，對手每個球員係每個陣式下會出現係咩位置，對手面對D咩陣式會打得差<br />\n<br />\n仲話對打比前，睇左51場打比既比賽；黎緊對史篤城，睇左對手新教練只前係盧頓26場比賽"},{"pid":"f0490972d7f9c8888031a2e02cc41ba05b483f22","tid":985403,"uid":2545,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T16:00:49.000Z","msg":"佢真係好撚痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今朝睇左篇野話佢係睇哂Derby上季總共40幾50場波<br />\n每場波大概用4粒鐘分析，然後summarize做15分鐘既野比自己隊波既每個球員快速理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果佢每隊